Coming to Game Preview 4/29 - Pre-install now with Game Pass!

The Belfry stands as a beacon of hope and safety amongst the ruins of humanity, where monsters lurk outside the tower’s walls. You are an Ace, born anew from the spirit realm with special skills, grit, and determination. Unite with other Aces*  in a thrilling venture into a new world to protect the people of the Belfry.

Can you become the Ace humanity needs to survive? Join us in Towerborne, a fast-paced, hope-filled, action RPG.  In this vibrant world with exhilarating combat, you’ll take on malevolent forces solo or alongside your companions* and fight as one.

Adventure Together – Venture out of The Belfry solo or with up to three other Aces* to vanquish the looming terror that surrounds the tower. Either way, you won’t be alone. author: Xbox
description:
Vercors Vendetta Mission and Weapons Pack OUT NOW! Also free for all players, Fairburne's Armory Weapons and Skins Pack!

Despite destroying the primary Nazi stockpile of the deadly nerve agent Kleine Blume, one final cache survived! This stash has now been loaded into artillery shells ready for an imminent launch against multiple targets throughout France. With millions of civilian lives at stake, Harry Hawker launches a daring attempt to neutralize the remaining Wunderwaffe before they can be deployed.

To help you complete your mission, the M1941 Rifle and Armaguerra OG-44 will be added to your arsenal. Used by the U.S Marine Corps, the M1941 is a powerful rifle with a 10-round high-capacity rotary magazine, requiring fewer reloads. Whereas the Italian Armaguerra OG-44 is a submachine gun that has a recoil mechanism housed above the barrel, resulting in extremely low vertical recoil.

The Vercors Vendetta Mission and Weapons Pack contains: 
• The Vercors Vendetta Campaign Mission
title: Sniper Elite: Resistance – Vercors Vendetta Mission and Weapons Pack DLC
